Class PlaceableItem

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bomb, CodeCard, Fuel, Garbage

    public class PlaceableItem
extends Item
implements java.lang.Comparable<Item>, java.lang.Cloneable
    Class father of all the items which can be located and taken from one place.
    It inherits from Item and add a no args contructor. Also it implements clone() and equals()
    It's not the purpose of this class create objects which interacts on the game, instead of it will be done with inherited classes of this. *@author Abel Serano Juste
